result:
.label-wrapper
    height 9rem
    overflow: scroll;
    .list
        display flex
        flex-wrap wrap
        .label-item
            margin: 0.2rem 0.3rem 0.1rem 0;
            padding: 0 0.2rem;
            background #EEEEEE
            color #282828
            border-radius 6px
            cursor pointer
            font-size 0.28rem
            height 0.56rem
            line-height 0.56rem
            &.on
                color #fff
                background #3875EA
.footer
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
.btn
    width 100%
    height 0.76rem
    border-radius: 43px;
    background #3875EA
.title
    font-size 0.32rem
    color #282828
